A COUPLE determined to take a romantic pic of themselves on
the ocean’s edge were lucky to come away in one piece after a giant wave
surprised them.Marelize Dreyer (25) and hubby Ryan Dreyer (26) were on
holiday in Hermanus earlier this month. Ryan explains in his blog how they
wanted to get “a perfect couple photo, the sea spray rising up behind us on the
rocks”.Instead, they got a video showing them being swept off
the rocks by the powerful wave!Marelize bust her leg in two places and dislocated her ankle, but is now on the
